OL,3,CAlderney's leading politician says
OL,4,Creview into economic deal is 'sensible'
OL,6,FHowever, accounts from 2023 suggest
OL,7,Fthat this arrangement may be unfair.
OL,9,FFigures from the accounts show that
OL,10,FGuernsey gave Alderney around #19
OL,11,Fmillion but only received #10.3
OL,12,Fmillion in return, something which is
OL,13,Fonly adding to Guernsey's ongoing
OL,14,Fdeficit.
OL,16,FOne of Alderney's biggest issues is
OL,17,Fthe upgrade needed for the island's
OL,18,Frunway and the uncertainty caused by
OL,19,FGuernsey opting to scale back its
OL,20,Fimprovement plans due to escalating
OL,21,Fcosts.
