OL,3,CAlderney's leading politician says
OL,4,Creview into economic deal is 'sensible'
OL,6,FDespite this ongoing debate, Mr Abel
OL,7,Finsists this is not the driving force
OL,8,Fbehind the review of the 1948
OL,9,Fagreement between the islands.
OL,11,FHe said: "We can look at this two
OL,12,Fways. One is sensible people doing
OL,13,Fsensible things. And the other is, is
OL,14,Fthere a political agenda here? From my
OL,15,Fpoint of view and from the point of
OL,16,Fview of Alderney's Policy and Finance
OL,17,FCommittee, we believe this is sensible
OL,18,Fpeople doing a sensible thing."
