OL,3,CAlderney's leading politician says
OL,4,Creview into economic deal is 'sensible'
OL,6,FHowever, one resident told ITV News
OL,7,Fthat if the commission carrying out
OL,8,Fthe review finds that there should be
OL,9,Fa reduction in the amount of money
OL,10,FAlderney gets, it could have a
OL,11,Fdevastating impact on the island.
OL,13,FOthers feel Alderney should look for
OL,14,Falternative ways to bring income into
OL,15,Fthe island and that reviewing the 1948
OL,16,Fagreement will give Alderney more
OL,17,Fclarity about how this can be done.
