OL,3,CAlderney's leading politician says
OL,4,Creview into economic deal is 'sensible'
OL,6,FJoanna Corder, said: "I find it very
OL,7,Fhard to believe that we are getting a
OL,8,Fgood deal at the moment because of the
OL,9,Fway that I feel that we are sometimes
OL,10,Ftreated by individuals in Guernsey,
OL,11,Fnot by the island as a whole.
OL,13,F"I appreciate the review because I
OL,14,Fhope it's going to show that everyone
OL,15,Fis doing their best (to get a fair
OL,16,Fdeal)."
