OL,6,FA Guernsey policy letter spoke about
OL,7,Fthe importance of holding the review,
OL,8,Fsaying: 'The Committee's view is that
OL,9,Fthe relationship between Guernsey and
OL,10,FAlderney should be resettled to ensure
OL,11,Fthat both sides have a clear and
OL,12,Fshared understanding of the parameters
OL,13,Fand reasonable expectations.
OL,15,F'The outcome of the review is unlikely
OL,16,Fto be decided until 2026 so until
OL,17,Fthen, it will remain Guernsey's
OL,18,Fresponsibility to maintain Alderney's
OL,19,Fairport and runway.'
