OL,6,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FLyndon Trott, said: ""Strong and
OL,8,Fresilient transport links are critical
OL,9,Fto the success of island communities.
OL,10,FHowever, we cannot ignore the
OL,11,Fchallenging fiscal situation that the
OL,12,FStates of
OL,14,FGuernsey finds itself in.
